.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, iris, aconite, sunflower
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, family, drama, epic, sports
City: rome, marseilles, boston, paris, liverpool
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: azaleamaster, july, june, april, december
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. the person watching animation movies is the person who growsiris
2. the person watching swedish movies is the owner of the dog
3. the person watching family movies is the person traveling to paris
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsaconite
5. the person who growsrose is the person traveling to marseilles
6. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the bird
7. the person who growssunflower is the person who's birthday is in july
8. the person traveling to boston is in the middle
9. the person watching epic movies is on the far left
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the owner of the cat
11. the owner of the horses is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july
12. the person who's birthday is in azaleamaster is the person traveling to rome
13. the person watching drama movies is the person who's birthday is in april
14. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea
15. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Flower		|    sunflower	|     azalea	|      iris	|     rose	|     aconite	|
| Movie-Genre	|   epic	|    family	|    animation	|    drama	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     cat	|    horse	|     bird	|     fish	|      dog	|
| City	|    liverpool	|     paris	|     boston	|    marseilles	|      rome	|
| Birthday		|   july	|    december	|  june	|    april	|   azaleamaster	|
